{
  "stem": "9995.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we are going among those-- those people shot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And it-- it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It-- it really was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "People who went early didn't see that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They just left one place of work after an another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But we were the one who later on were cleaning also that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And then some people were still hidden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Now, my husband managed-- oh, he going to tell you this probably, most likely.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was putting them in a big place and was getting them out of ghetto if he found them, but otherwise the Germans were shooting them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And whichever room we went, when we were cleaning ghetto, it was blood all over the place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It-- it was so-- you know, I saw one German taking a child, and taking him by his legs, and ripping him up to here and throwing against the wall.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They were all fathers and-- and-- and brothers and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And to do such thing!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It's incomprehend.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "If I wouldn't see it, I wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it was so bad that I never saw a movie or anything which would, in-- in the brutality of this thing, which would be similar to-- to what was going on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I believe that even the pogroms which happened you know, on Ukraine, and over, could not have been as bad as what this was there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Country of-- of Goethe, of Schiller, of Beethoven, and all the great Germans, and that's how they behaved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It-- it was-- they actually were persuaded that we were [NON-ENGLISH], and they were the supermen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "However, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] now, here, people are protesting if you killed little animal and make a fur coat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But still, killing people, it's still going on, the terrorism and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
